about ICT innovations

4
00:00:14,895 --> 00:00:17,077
for emergency response.

5
00:00:17,428 --> 00:00:20,774
Talking about technologies 
for disaster response management,

6
00:00:20,774 --> 00:00:25,532
I think we need to start looking
into, first and foremost, how communities

7
00:00:25,532 --> 00:00:29,151
use technology and what technology
is in the hands of communities today.

8
00:00:29,493 --> 00:00:32,254
Obviously, this question
cannot be answered

9
00:00:32,254 --> 00:00:36,224
without talking about
the role of mobile technology

10
00:00:36,224 --> 00:00:38,824
and how mobile technology
has revolutionized

11
00:00:38,824 --> 00:00:41,493
the way we understand the world
and the way we communicate,

12
00:00:41,493 --> 00:00:44,484
the way people are able
to coordinate around response,

13
00:00:44,484 --> 00:00:47,538
share information and start
organizing their own response.

14
00:00:48,424 --> 00:00:51,754
There are more mobile phones
than people today.

15
00:00:51,754 --> 00:00:55,364
And I think mobile phones
have helped people tremendously

16
00:00:55,364 --> 00:01:00,584
to share information that is critical
