we are looking at interconnected devices
that are able to transfer data.

57
00:03:08,233 --> 00:03:14,244
I think we still need to really
make a strong point

58
00:03:14,244 --> 00:03:17,734
for so-called traditional technology
such as radio.

59
00:03:17,734 --> 00:03:22,395
Being FM radio or shortwave radio,
in many countries around the world

60
00:03:22,395 --> 00:03:25,214
is still the technology
