62
00:03:28,979 --> 00:03:32,640
in terms of sharing life saving,
useful and actionable information

63
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:34,499
for disaster affected communities.

64
00:03:34,509 --> 00:03:38,018
This also helps create spaces
for dialogue between local communities

65
00:03:38,018 --> 00:03:40,088
and responders.

66
00:03:40,088 --> 00:03:45,588
