71
00:04:03,439 --> 00:04:06,476
It's also about creating
a two-way communication

72
00:04:06,476 --> 00:04:09,459
between local communities
and disaster responders.

73
00:04:09,781 --> 00:04:15,187
I think we need to
put at the center of anything we do,

74
00:04:15,187 --> 00:04:16,879
local communities themselves.

75
00:04:16,879 --> 00:04:22,569
One of the interesting turns
of events in recent years

76
00:04:22,569 --> 00:04:27,939
is to reinvigorate the discussion
