77
00:04:27,942 --> 00:04:30,072
as disaster responders,

78
00:04:30,072 --> 00:04:32,852
as communities who always respond first.

79
00:04:33,155 --> 00:04:38,765
It is interesting that we are calling
attention to this particular issue

80
00:04:38,765 --> 00:04:41,285
because it has always been like that.

81
00:04:41,743 --> 00:04:45,561
As an interesting part 
that technology brings

82
00:04:45,561 --> 00:04:49,402
into this equation is that
finally it seems that we are

83
00:04:49,402 --> 00:04:53,124
paying more attention to all the different
questions and capacities

84
00:04:53,124 --> 00:04:54,262
that people always had.

85
00:04:54,262 --> 00:04:57,292
The difference is that 40 or 50 years ago
in Biafra, people didn't have

86
00:04:57,292 --> 00:05:00,870
the opportunities to make
their voices heard that they have today--

87
00:05:01,010 --> 00:05:03,658
