in places like the Philippines,

88
00:05:03,658 --> 00:05:06,170
in places like Yemen.

89
00:05:06,580 --> 00:05:13,070
There's been a-- particularly since Haiti,
even though people getting online

90
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:16,742
and collaborating is not something
