107
00:06:19,753 --> 00:06:22,804
From disaster preparedness
and disaster management perspective,

108
00:06:22,804 --> 00:06:27,343
I think the challenge for communities
is to actually go through

109
00:06:27,343 --> 00:06:29,734
what is good from what is accurate.

110
00:06:29,957 --> 00:06:35,869
One of the most important factors
to take into consideration is that, yes,

111
00:06:35,869 --> 00:06:37,935
the world is a much more 
interconnected place,

112
00:06:37,935 --> 00:06:40,105
but do we know better,
do we know more?

113
00:06:40,105 --> 00:06:44,628
So it is important to look into 
connectivity and access to social media,

114
00:06:44,628 --> 00:06:49,104
not just as a good in it's own right,
